Invocation Name: quick snacks
des: This will give you new daily ideas for snacks you can make in 20 minutes or less and take on the go during the work week. These are all reduced calorie recipes and great for anyone too busy to cook breakfast or lunch. Perfect for at the desk or on the move these snacks are healthy and easy.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
